
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-mack-crane-l2vpn-spb-o-mpls-00.txt'>
    <title>"Shortest Path Bridging (SPB) over an MPLS Packet Switched Network", Ben Mack-Crane, Lucy Yong</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-mack-crane-l2vpn-spb-o-mpls-00.txt</link>
    <description>This informational document describes ways to interconnect a Shortest Path Tree (SPT) Region over WAN connections using MPLS Pseudo Wires (PWs) with existing SPB and MPLS standards. It also describes how a combination of SPB and MPLS can provide a hierarchical scalable L2VPN.</description>
    <dc:date>2011-10-19T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
